 16 August 1916 Wednesday Janet 's birthday ! ! ! Out in the battlefield . Return to Casualti Corner at 7 a.m. breakfast( ? ) short ration Seek "possi " in dugout rest all day . Dugout chat billet chat wage war on my back . Can't sleep for gun continu bombard overhead . Incident of boy die at Casualti Corner wound in chest . Aeroplan . Fritzi has 8 balloon 3 taub up . We have 20 odd aeroplan by day . Incident of boy die at Casualti Corner . Poor lad so quick he went out . stay in dugout all night . Slept fair well .
